channel.title: ~Need Coder For Vscape~
channel.description:
Can anyone help me code my server? If you are willing to help code for me, then you get Administration status and Co-Leader status. Talk to me about it on my MSN: xbc_playa@hotmail.com
Please help me, I need someone like you to make my server better.
Remember, you always get something out of it.
(PS: My server is Hamachi based, since Port-Forwarding on my computer does not work, therefore please do not change your mind in helping me if it's Hamachi based.)
Thanks again, and remember to always contact me if you are willing to help.
Thanks!
